==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Clannish
<hw>Clan"nish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
a clan; closely united, like a clan; disposed to associate only with
one's clan or clique; actuated by the traditions, prejudices, habits,
etc., of a clan.</def></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Clan"nish*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>clan"nish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>clannishness</ent>⟦br⟧
